{"tid":1925052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"最新一集繼續寸PK鄧","createTime":"2020-03-14T06:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T09:16:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"72c272160c6bd6b7567dc3d7f231ed19a68f6a14","tid":1925052,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:00:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200314/NTXL4L23JG72RMGIVGP22ZTTR4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200314%2FNTXL4L23JG72RMGIVGP22ZTTR4%2F&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=09e6d962\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200314%2FNTXL4L23JG72RMGIVGP22ZTTR4%2F&h=9fa937cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200314/NTXL4L23JG72RMGIVGP22ZTTR4/</a><br />\n<br />\n最新一集繼續寸PK鄧<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】收到逾三萬宗讚賞的《頭條新聞》，昨晚如常在港台31頻道播出，吳志森及曾志豪繼續扮嘢寸爆政府，「頭盤」為派薄口罩給DSE考生，更以確診影星湯漢斯主演的名片《阿甘正傳》中的名句來抽水，改成「生命就好似a box of口罩，你永遠唔知道抽到厚定薄嘅」。再提到武漢肺炎的命名被指污衊了該地名，兩人翻出去年元朗7.21事件的賬，將之命名為「YL20190721」，十分抵死。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：網民力撐  9日增7萬Like<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200314/large/1584117368_7e2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200314%2Flarge%2F1584117368_7e2c.jpg&h=d28e60d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王喜節目內的〈驚方訊息〉繼續保留。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暗嘲訓斥警員做法<br />\n<br />\n曾志豪其後擊鼓，指有區議員要求警員道歉，但他帶出警方不懂得道歉，原因是「一嚟我哋衙差做事光明磊落，其次大帥對我哋好嚴厲，有啲乜事就訓斥，而唔係講對唔住。」暗嘲警務處處長鄧炳強處理警員的手法。節目下半部，吳志森與曾志豪所扮演的太后和徐副官再出擊，多次提到中國提出「世界欠中國一個道歉」及「世界欠中國一聲感謝」，又稱有指疫情源自美國及軍人，故該改名為「流美軍」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，曾志豪於商台節目《903獨立調查委員》被問到，《頭條》所受到的限制和壓迫有多少，他以《聖經》故事《所羅門的審判》來比喻，嘆現時圍繞港台的團體，沒有一個真心愛錫港台，更沒有主持公道的話事人。<br />\n<br />\n曾志豪又指出：「我哋好似見唔到會有一個充滿智慧嘅所羅門王企喺度。如果你問我邊個最有資格做嗰個所羅門王，唔係任何位高權貴嘅人，而係公眾─聽眾同埋觀眾。」"},{"pid":"d833763c1a05b2d25befd3fa186dffdd1a34f8ee","tid":1925052,"uid":174432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:04:12.000Z","msg":"驚訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7648e29b930b9b09f7d8b7c9d1f2a7dbcfe647d0","tid":1925052,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"Pusu"},{"pid":"a07f5f34663942446afbe4ba9627bc4cfeabe7fa","tid":1925052,"uid":125623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:53:06.000Z","msg":"每集都要睇幾次先夠皮"},{"pid":"17e5e25a6e7a94ca51365f98e4c6fbb58cae8691","tid":1925052,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IMsvG-DwtNo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIMsvG-DwtNo&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=c5d7c5ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IMsvG-DwtNo</a>"}]}